data.name: Label4.Text
data.value: The current spark plug is directly connected to the ignition coil, and the pulsed high-voltage electricity generated by the ignition coil is discharged, which penetrates the air between the two electrodes of the spark plug, and generates an electric spark to ignite the fuel-gas mixture in the cylinder. MAPMS spark plugs meet the requirements of thermal property, tensile strength, heat resistance, electrical conductivity, dielectric strength, sealing, and corrosion resistance. Spark plugs are mounted on the side or top of the engine

data.name: Label5.Text
data.value: LED headlights are used to illuminate the road in front of the car when driving at night, and are symmetrically installed on both sides of the front end of the vehicle. There are two-lamp and four-lamp systems. In four-lamp system, headlamps are installed side by side, a pair of low-beam and high-beam lamps are installed on the outside, a pair of single high-beam lamps are installed on the inside.
